Car manufacturer Mahindra South Africa (SA) has appointed Rajesh Gupta to succeed Sanjoy Gupta as CEO. Sanjoy Gupta will resume the role of customer care automotive division VP at Mahindra in India. Mahindra SA stated on Friday that Rajesh Gupta has 19 yearsâ€™ experience in spearheading marketing and sales operations across various industries. He has also served in leading multinational corporate setups in plant bio-technology, logistics and automobile industries. He joined Mahindra at a crucial juncture, the company noted, considering its introduction of several new products in the passenger segment as well as the recent launch of its Mahindra pickup truck.